15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n佢老母有無幫你吹返首碧海潮生曲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d857c07c46b4caec5d4806ff4448b6992bd26534","tid":420462,"uid":12736,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:15:45.000Z","msg":"1943年西班牙國王盃準決賽。在首回合，巴塞在主場贏了皇馬3:0。由於皇馬代表政府，巴塞就代表反政府，所以佛朗哥絕不容許皇馬大敗於巴塞腳下，若果這種情況出現，可能會動搖到他的政權及威信，所以他要出手了。他派國家的保安官員訪問巴塞，然後威迫利誘。在生命受到威脅之下，巴塞球員就範，在次回合，皇馬以11:1大勝巴塞。<br />\n<br />\n重有賤種J個5連歐聯咪又係佛朗哥夾硬係巴搶迪史提芬奴過去<br />\n根本成間球會係極權既代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e8ee76faae3c51a3fb1156ba296dc474f58660","tid":420462,"uid":1903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:17:17.000Z","msg":"第一次認同老鼠"},{"pid":"4380dfe13f1494631c1b7d9c00c5caa110d47cee","tid":420462,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"反疤但撐加獨又點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7dd43c53faa297019cefa45c4a637e8392c3fb0","tid":420462,"uid":130419,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1943年西班牙國王盃準決賽。在首回合，巴塞在主場贏了皇馬3:0。由於皇馬代表政府，巴塞就代表反政府，所以佛朗哥絕不容許皇馬大敗於巴塞腳下，若果這種情況出現，可能會動搖到他的政權及威信，所以他要出手了。他派國家的保安官員訪問巴塞，然後威迫利誘。在生命受到威脅之下，巴塞球員就範，在次回合，皇馬以11:1大勝巴塞。<br />\n<br />\n重有賤種J個5連歐聯咪又係佛朗哥夾硬係巴搶迪史提芬奴過去<br />\n根本成間球會係極權既代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西甲主席同偑雷斯又咁撚熟<br />\n係巴盛世果陣搞埋啲小動作 有一年巴係上半季啲賽程要踢晒西甲前8名既主場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n皇馬因球證得益既比賽當冇事 巴因球證得益既比賽就罰果個球證<br />\n上年貝迪斯對巴塞個球證吹錯間接令巴失分就拎上界最佳球證 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}